name: cool boys team
description: clothingline created by my six year old son paulie..he said dad only certain kids are on the cool boy team. I asked him what the cool boy team was and what you have to do to be on the cool boy team,he said "dad you have to just be a good kid". so hear is his and his brothers college money..

name: welcome to spacecamp the official 20 track album
description: 20 banging tracks that lead you on a rollercoaster of emotion, with hit club songs, nice motivation songs, crazy witty mad punch lines, creative flows like jet skis over  water,,heavy street anthems to rock and jock arena jamz..all in house production  with beats from dj genius,deborahs son,paulie n cash productions and a couple features from some of the biggest names to hit the game like b.delaney, shaliek rivers, slang d etc..this action packed classic will have you once again saying BRING THAT BACK DID YOU HEAR WHAT HE JUST SAID!!
